\c 12
\s Ingoma yokubonga
\p
\v 1 Langalolosuku\x + 2.11.\x* uzakuthi: Ngiyakubonga, N\nd kosi\nd*, lanxa wawungithukuthelele, ulaka lwakho seluphendukile, njalo ungiduduzile.
\v 2 Khangela, uNkulunkulu ulusindiso lwami\x + Hlab. 38.22. Hlab. 18.2.\x*, ngizathemba ngingesabi; ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* uJehova\x + 26.4. Hlab. 68.4.\x* ingamandla ami lengoma yami\x + Eks. 15.2. Hlab. 118.14. Hlab. 59.17.\x*, isibe lusindiso lwami.
\v 3 Ngakho ngentokozo\x + Joha. 7.37,38.\x* lizakukha amanzi emithonjeni yosindiso.
\v 4 Lithi ngalolosuku\x + 2.11.\x*: Bongani iN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 1 Lan. 16.8. Hlab. 105.1.\x*, libize ibizo layo\x + 1 Lan. 16.8. Hlab. 105.1.\x*, lazise izenzo zayo\x + 1 Lan. 16.8. Hlab. 105.1.\x*\x + Hlab. 145.4-6.\x* phakathi kwezizwe, limemezele ukuthi ibizo layo\x + Hlab. 148.13.\x* liphakeme\x + Zaga 18.10.\x*.
\v 5 Hlabelelani eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + Eks. 15.1,21. Hlab. 98.1.\x* ngoba yenzile izinto ezinhle kakhulu; lokhu kakwaziwe emhlabeni wonke.
\v 6 Memeza\x + 54.1. 10.30.\x*, uhlabele ngentokozo, mhlali weZiyoni\x + 54.1. 10.30.\x*\x + Zef. 3.14. Zek. 9.9.\x*, ngoba oNgcwele kaIsrayeli mkhulu phakathi kwakho\x + 5.24. 41.14,16. Hlab. 71.22.\x*\x + Hlab. 46.5.\x*.